  "title": "Core Utilities",
  "description": "A futuristic tech-meets-automation mod for Minecraft, designed to expand the game’s core functionality with high-efficiency tools, modular machines, and directional logic systems.",
  "body": "<!-- Header Images -->\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wBTP1tg.png\" alt=\"Banner 1\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto;\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- Social Links -->\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n    <a href=\"https://discord.gg/TJc3CxR4jK\" style=\"margin:4px;\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Discord&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&logoColor=white\"></a>\n    <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@nightbeamstudio\" style=\"margin:4px;\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=YouTube&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=youtube&logoColor=white\"></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/sponsors/MeherBenSalem\" style=\"margin:4px;\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=GitHub&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=github&logoColor=white\"></a>\n    <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/nightbeamstudio/projects\" style=\"margin:4px;\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=CurseForge&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&logoColor=white\"></a>\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/organization/nightbeam\" style=\"margin:4px;\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Modrinth&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&logoColor=white\"></a>\n    <a href=\"https://nightbeam.gitbook.io/core-utils/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Documentation&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=read-the-docs&logoColor=white\"></a>\n</p>\n\n<!-- About Section -->\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/about.png\" alt=\"About Header\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto;\">\n</p>\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/fpQbjT-qUbQ\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center; max-width:900px; margin:0 auto 50px auto; font-size:1.1em; line-height:1.6;\">\n    <strong>Core Utilities</strong> is a futuristic, tech-driven utility mod inspired by \n    <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/extra-utilities\"><em>Extra Utilities</em></a> and \n    <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/dark-utilities\"><em>Dark Utilities</em></a>. \n    It expands Minecraft’s automation, energy, and logistics systems with modular machines, advanced conduits, and functional design — all in a clean, pixel-art, Minecraft-faithful style.\n</p>\n\n<!-- Ko-fi Donation Button -->\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom:40px;\">\n    <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/nightbeamstudio\" target=\"_blank\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5c14e387dab576fe667689cf/670f5a0171bfb928b21a7e00_support_me_on_kofi_beige.png\" alt=\"Support on Ko-fi\" width=\"220\" style=\"border-radius:8px; box-shadow:0px 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\">\n    </a>\n</p>\n\n<!-- Features Section -->\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top:50px;\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/features.png\" alt=\"Features Header\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; margin-bottom:20px;\">\n</p>\n\n<ul style=\"max-width:900px; margin:0 auto 50px auto; font-size:1.1em; line-height:1.6;\">\n    <li><strong>Vector Plates:</strong> Move entities with configurable speed and direction (<span style=\"color:#e67e23;\">medium</span>/<span style=\"color:#e03e2d;\">fast</span>/<span style=\"color:#ba372a;\">very_fast</span>).</li>\n    <li><strong>Effect Plates:</strong> Affect mobs and players on contact (regen, speed, poison, etc.).</li>\n    <li><strong>Filter Blocks:</strong> Only filtered types can pass (right-click with a wrench to reverse).</li>\n    <li><strong>Floating Block:</strong> Can be placed anywhere.</li>\n    <li><strong>Backpacks:</strong> Three tiers with 27 / 54 / 100 slots.</li>\n    <li><strong>Mob Net:</strong> Catch and release mobs.</li>\n    <li><strong>Configuration Wrench:</strong> Tool to configure machines and blocks.</li>\n    <li><strong>Solar Panel:</strong> Generates FE based on daylight.</li>\n    <li><strong>Cables:</strong> Transfer FE energy (64/tick).</li>\n</ul>\n\n<!-- Installation Section -->\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top:50px;\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/installation.png\" alt=\"Installation Header\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; margin-bottom:20px;\">\n</p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:center; max-width:900px; margin:0 auto 50px auto;\">\n    <p><strong>⏩ Compatible Versions:</strong> Minecraft 1.16.5 → 1.21.8</p>\n    <p><strong>⏩ Requirements:</strong> NeoForge or Forge, JAUMl Library</p>\n</div>\n",
